description:
Surf is a mobile app development studio that focuses on exceptional solutions for various businesses. We specialise in iOS & Android full-cycle development, we use Big Data and Machine Learning to create effective products for our clients. Our main areas of expertise are e-commerce, retail and banking.
Surf is one of 24 agencies in the world certified by Google. We stay ahead of the curve and get access to new technologies way before they become popular.
We aim to build apps that transform our clients’ businesses and improve IT industry in general.       
Our strengths:
Personal approach to cooperation — we listen to our clients carefully, understand their needs, help them build the right strategy and deliver solutions on time;
Product-based approach to development — we analyze, invent, design and develop; we control the quality and continuously improve the product;
Design and development harmony — we pay equal attention to usability, UI design, efficient code and solid architecture based on modern technologies;
Agile — we work iteratively to deliver solid results;
Full transparency: our clients always know everything about the team, pricing model and stages of product development;
Great experience — we successfully delivered more than 100 projects. 
